Technologies:
Nodejs, Expressjs, React, MongoDB

Features:
1. User can create an account.
2. User can create work items.
3. User can update the work items.
4. User can view the work items.
5. User can generate reports.
6. System can send out notifications for inactive work items.

Entities: 
1. User
2. AccountManager
3. ActionItem
4. ActionItemManager
5. ProgressNotes
6. Reports
7. Notifications
8. Projects

Entities in Detail:

1. User
    DataMembers:
        1. username
        2. password
        3. first name
        4. last name
        5. email
        6. userID
    DataFunctions:
        1. getUser()

2. Account
    DataMembers:
        1. List of Users
    DataFunction:
        1. addUser()
        2. updateUser()
        3. deleteUser()

3. ActionItems
    DataMembers:
        1. Enum of status
            a.
        2. Enum of stages
        2. List of ProgressNotes
        3. Name
        4. Collaborators
        5. Current Status
        6. Project Name
        7. User ID
        8. Project ID
    DataFunctions:
        1. getWorkItem()
        2. addUserToAI()
        3. removeUserToAI()
        4. getUserOfAI()
        5. getStatus()
        6. updateStatus()
        7. getName()
        8. updateName()
        9. addProgressNotes()
        10. removeProgressNotes()
        11. getListOfProgressNotes()
        12. getProjectName()
        13. updateProjectName()

4. ActionItemManager
    DataMembers:
    DataFunction:
        1. getActionItems()
        2. addActionItems()
        3. removeActionItems()

5. ProgressNote
    DataMembers:
        1. Text(desc/update)
        2. Images
        3. Links
    DataFunctions:
        1. getPNDetails()
        2. addImages()
        3. removeImages()
        4. addLinks()
        5. removeLinks()
        6. getDesc()
        7. updateDesc()

6. Report
    DataMembers:
    DataFunctions:
        1. getAIBasedOnTime()
        2. getAIBasedOnStatus()
        3. prepareReportBasedOnTime()
        4. prepareReportBasedOnStatus()

7. Notification
    DataMembers:
    DataFunctions:  
        1. sendMailWithReport()
        2. sendMailForInactiveAI()
        
8. Projects
    Data Members:
        1. name
        2. userId

